sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant PasswordUtils
participant DB
participant JWT

User->>Frontend: Submit password change
Frontend->>API: POST /api/auth/change-password
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: authRateLimit
alt Rate limited
API-->>Frontend: 429 Too many requests
Frontend-->>User: Show rate limit message
else Allowed
API->>API: Validate current_password and new_password
alt Missing fields
API-->>Frontend: 400 current_password and new_password are required
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Provided
alt New password same as current
API-->>Frontend: 400 New password must be different
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Different passwords
API->>PasswordUtils: getPasswordValidationError(new_password)
alt Password validation fails
PasswordUtils-->>API: error message
API-->>Frontend: 400 validation error
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Password valid
API->>DB: Query employee by id (primary schema)
alt Primary query error
alt ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR
DB-->>API: error code ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR
API->>DB: Query employee by id (legacy schema)
alt Fallback error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
else Fallback success
DB-->>API: rows
end
else Other DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
end
else Primary query success
DB-->>API: rows
end
API->>API: Check if employee exists
alt Not found
API->>API: clear auth cookie
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authenticated user was not found
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Found
API->>PasswordUtils: verifyPassword(stored, current_password)
alt Password mismatch
PasswordUtils-->>API: matched = false
API-->>Frontend: 401 Current password is incorrect
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Password match
API->>PasswordUtils: hashPassword(new_password)
API->>DB: Update password (fallback on ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR)
API->>JWT: sign token
API->>API: set auth cookie
API-->>Frontend: 200 Password changed successfully
Frontend-->>User: Show success
end
end
end
end
end
end
end
